query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND n.gender in ('f') AND (chn.name like '%Wonder Woman%' OR chn.name like '%T-800%' OR chn.name like '%Rocky Balboa%' OR chn.name like '%Jack Torrance%' OR chn.name like '%Hannibal Lecter%') AND mi_idx.info > '6.0' AND it2.info in ('plot','LD disc format','admissions','gross','taglines','LD dynamic range','LD picture format','alternate versions','LD digital sound','portrayed in','LD status of availablility','LD sharpness','mpaa') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','complete+verified','cast') AND cct1.kind in ('cast','complete+verified','crew') AND k.keyword not like '%terror%' AND k.keyword not like '%magic%' AND k.keyword not like '%future%' AND k.keyword not like '%history%' AND k.keyword not like '%chase%' AND kt.kind in ('episode','video game','movie','tv movie','video movie','tv mini series') AND (t.title like '%window%' OR t.title like '%dream%' OR t.title like '%letter%')
